title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 5 categories of Response on the x axis representing 3 groups: 2011, 2012, and 2013.
Averaging these 3 groups, the highest category is found for Response Spend the same as last Christmas with a mean value of 46.0.
Followed by Spend less than last Christmas with a mean value of 33.0.
The lowest category is observed at Do not celebrate Christmas that has a mean value of 3.67
showing a difference of 170.5% with the maximum value.

In case of Spend the same as last Christmas, 2011 shows more dominance than any other Response and it has the lowest value in Do not celebrate Christmas. On the other hand, group 2012 is the second impactful group in this chart, and it's highest in case of Spend the same as last Christmas and has the minimum dominance for Response Do not celebrate Christmas.
